mirkwood.c


print_fine_time("Starting the exposure");
suc=0;
while (suc != 1) {
/* Send the SEX command */
ret = doCommand(pci_fd, TIM_ID, SEX, DON);
if (ret != 0) {
fcntl(0, F_SETFL, flags); /* restore the flags */
printf("Error: SEX command returns \"%x\"", getError());
return(ret);
}
